{"tid":29022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"🐱急求愛貓人士俾貓b一個家","createTime":"2016-12-08T10:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:39:27.000Z","uid":19159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aff7b02302507f9a306032ea62c685c6df3eed03","tid":29022,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日朋友係街度執左一隻流浪貓bb 因為我返緊工用唔到電話 佢又唔知點做好就帶左去SPCA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你知SPCA既貓仔幾難先上到領養部架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我打左電話去問下貓貓情況。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貓貓健康 痴人 已杜蟲打針 <span style=\"color: red;\">搵緊暫養家庭 無需家訪 只要提供地址 證明非無住屋人士或工場、籠屋就ok！</span> 好希望你地有人可以暫養佢！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Case No. Telegram我話你知 怕有人搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛協電話 28020501</span><br />\n<br />\n我屋企兩隻貓16號絕育 唔可以暫養佢<br />\n愛協表示 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願意暫養之家庭 愛協會提供貓糧、貓砂、及睇醫生的全數費用！過左兩星期俾醫生檢查完可以直接領養或由他人領養</span></span><br />\n大家都知貓b好難上到領養部 求大家 呢到個個都好人黎 幫手暫養 不用家訪仲免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrP0X92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrP0X92.jpg&h=7fbfffda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0pE233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0pE233.jpg&h=1eee063d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影得唔清楚 但朋友話同我隻貓好似樣好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb577b40687b8f127c2edc5f6c942decd49eb6ff","tid":29022,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"我Telegram： thisismyphone"},{"pid":"48f0840779a905ee5d5a1737b038442717044